Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima-sensei, why do you want to perform\Nat the Culture Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.91,0:00:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got this horrible friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And since she's feeling so sorry for herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to punch her, just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's when I got the feeling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That something might change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's a cute kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kousei Arima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With Aiza's little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he her big brother's rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't he retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elohim, Essaim... Elohim, Essaim...\NI implore you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, good. Couldn't have\N gotten off to a better start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've got to be kidding me.\NIn the short time that I hadn't seen her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's gotten incredibly good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagi... good luck!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was all stiff from nerves,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but my fingers are moving.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can hear both my own playing,\Nand Arima-sensei's playing, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that practice didn't lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't concentrate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can still hear the sound of the piano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's in my way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're in my way, so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get out of here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just now... the sound...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound... changed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you doing?\N What are you thinking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're supposed to be supporting me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So why are you dumping\N all this pressure on me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Liar! Fraud! Moron! This is totally different\Nfrom the way we practiced!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both the rhythm,\Nand this aching sense of atmosphere...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every last thing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Kousei Arima, pianist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The tempo's starting to take off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's playing the bass,\Nbut he's starting to consume the melody.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you going to do, Nagi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you going to let Kousei\Nhave his way with you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, settle it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bring it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's not giving in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amazing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aiza's kid sister is competing with him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how he goads her, or how he\Ndrags her along in his wake, she's keeping up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was she always this good?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:57.40,BTSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Connected
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right, Nagi. You're the star of this stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't even give him an inch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... in a waltz...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The melody shifts to the bottom part!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not getting away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen closely!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respond simultaneously!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be enveloped by Kousei Arima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two months ago, I would've been left behind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that time... didn't go to waste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time I devoted to playing the piano...\Nis paying off now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's got a heart of steel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's like a robot, isn't he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a Chogokin robot, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're wrong about that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei Arima is no Chogokin robot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He doesn't have a heart of steel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I touched it, his hand was warm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment I touched it...\Nthat moment... was so nostalgic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the bass line player, he's magnificent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He knows her personality,\Nhe's grasped her habits, he's goading her,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}leading her on, and backing her up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's putting his partner in the zone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's accelerating her growth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those roasted sweet potatoes\N we shared sure were good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those pork buns we had on our way home...\Nthey sure were good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is, without a doubt... their waltz.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only started playing the piano because\NI wanted my beloved big brother's attention.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An ulterior motive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for the last few weeks,\NI've been peering into the abyss, just a little bit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I cried, I vomited,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I went without food or sleep\Nto immerse myself in music.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it was so painful... so painful\Nto look my powerless self in the eye,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that I wanted to run away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You felt the same way, didn't you, brother?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's important to play for someone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you know what...\Nthat's not what I want to see!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't lose your way! Don't struggle! Step on it!\NActions, not words! Don't stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not in you to lose your way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run up those stairs like you're skipping lightly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like you did that day... once again,\Nmake yourself chase after that back of his!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My hero!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... Just like Nagi saw herself in you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you've been seeing yourself in Nagi, haven't you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Kousei?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unlike everybody else,\NI don't yearn to become a pro,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I'm not prepared to give\Nall of myself to music,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but there are people who will listen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are people I want to play for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are people that I love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So... I want to be here. Is that wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't that a good enough reason\Nto want to play, for now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I doing here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I doing, looking up at\N the stage from the audience?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm supposed to be up there, aren't I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Emi and Nagi...\Nwhy does your playing move people...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Arima?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's about to end. Ah... it feels so weird.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm exhausted,\Nbut I want to go on playing till I collapse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I play it right?\NWas I able to confront it with sincerity?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Arima-sensei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are the sounds you make so colorful,\Nand so beautiful?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so beautiful that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I'm gonna cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, acknowledge them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the months of agony, screaming,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}suffering and struggling...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aiza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a moment\Nwhen you're rewarded for all that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Music just might transcend words.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima-sensei? Do you think it reached him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It reached him. I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Arima-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to give her that punch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A performance that won't be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Christine. The girl who yearns\Nto go onstage at the opera house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even as she lost her way and suffered,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,big-bro complex and all,\NNagi climbed up that stairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you planning to sit around\Ntwiddling your thumbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you get anything from that?\NFrom Nagi's performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to just sit tight here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a great duet you played!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't move me one bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki... Komugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not the one who's amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are an ultra-sadist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't music fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it too thrilling for words,\Nwatching somebody grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's why you placed that kid\Nunder my wing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know what,\Nsince you guys started coming over,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been enjoying myself\Nlike there's no tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Arima!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're Bushi... Aiza...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Takeshi! Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, don't grab hold of my kid sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kid sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce him. This is my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But Aizato, your last name's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please! I introduced\N myself properly, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm Nagi Aiza!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I said it right, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So I misheard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm glad you're so dense.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that! Why the hell\Nwere you playing a duet with Nagi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I... I asked Nagi, as a favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,None of that "Nagi" business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean "Takeshi's little sister!"\NDon't you dare look at her as a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, You're killing me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut that out, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? You defending Arima?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, how'd you\Nget to know Arima, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking after me here.\NHe's teaching me all kinds of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All kinds of...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's giving me all these precious experiences!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Experiences!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,December.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Eastern Japan Piano Competition will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's where I'm gonna\Ngive you a beatdown, got that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bring it on! I'm gonna do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flaunting something like that before my eyes...\NHow can I just let that go unanswered!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man. December's gonna be\Na pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One-tenth... even one one-hundredth...\NDid my feelings get through to him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did my music reach him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... very... much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:39.86,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aiza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the heck? He's never even\N said a word to me before...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the heck is going on here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:17:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aiza... Wh-Why were you\Nplaying a duet with Kousei... Arima?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Kousei Arima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Kousei Arima"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't you dare\Ndrop the honorifics for Arima-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna pull your hair out,\N you damned midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:14.73,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damned midget! Damned midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!? What kind\Nof relationship is that!? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So do you have his contact info!?\NHis email address, too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do!\NYesterday, we had taiyaki together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was so yummy, that taiyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.12,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Arima
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know his email address...\NThe taiyaki was yummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You knowing Arima... that's so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkle, twinkle, little star...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How I wonder what you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:51.14,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:18:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkle, twinkle, little star...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How I wonder what you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Up above the world so high...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like a diamond in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkle, twinkle, li–
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that guy your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's what\Nyou call a jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean a jackass!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Making a violinist who can't play\Nthe violin listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's your fault that I miss it now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't commit double suicide with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:19:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look, when we went shopping,\NI was the one who carried your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You always take the initiative.\NYou only tell me things after the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You walk in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm always behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I always remember...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is seeing you from behind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it wouldn't be double suicide,\NI'd be following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So please, give me one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me another chance\Nto stand by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please perform with me one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the daughter of a cake shop owner\Nwho loves canelés,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you're not the heroine of a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I ever gonna play Ravel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So please, perform with me one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're the one who said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“Do you think you'll be able to forget?”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you knew that. I'm a jackass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The air is chilly, and as dry as can be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The laundered sheets\Nlend a gentleness to my surroundings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such a cruel boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Telling me to dream one more time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I was satisfied\Nbecause my dream had come true...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'd told myself it was enough...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yet here you are,\Nwatering this withered heart again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're making her cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a vile jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy of women!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that's not what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, jackass!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boys aren't supposed to bully girls, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm greedy, so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just gonna dream again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of waltzing with you someday...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:19.97,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hearts Come Together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just might.{\i0}
